{"title":"Hello World","date":"2020-02-10T07:24:38.789Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Feb 10, 2020","L":"02/10/2020","MM-DD":"02-10"},"link":"2020/02/10/hello-world","updated":"2020-02-09T08:37:05.000Z","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\" target=\"_blank\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\" target=\"_blank\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\" target=\"_blank\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"quick-start\">Quick Start<a href=\"#quick-start\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"create-a-new-post\">Create a new post<a href=\"#create-a-new-post\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">\"My New Post\"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\" target=\"_blank\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"run-server\">Run server<a href=\"#run-server\" title=\"Run server\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\" target=\"_blank\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"generate-static-files\">Generate static files<a href=\"#generate-static-files\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\" target=\"_blank\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites<a href=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html\" target=\"_blank\">Deployment</a></p>\n","prev":{"title":"django_doc_read","link":"2020/03/24/django_doc_read"},"next":{"title":"Fastdfs doc","link":"2020/02/10/Fastdfs doc"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2020/02/10/hello-world/","toc":[{"id":"quick-start","title":"Quick Start","index":"1","children":[{"id":"create-a-new-post","title":"Create a new post","index":"1.1"},{"id":"run-server","title":"Run server","index":"1.2"},{"id":"generate-static-files","title":"Generate static files","index":"1.3"},{"id":"deploy-to-remote-sites","title":"Deploy to remote sites","index":"1.4"}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://yoursite.com/2020/02/10/hello-world/\" title=\"Hello World\">http://yoursite.com/2020/02/10/hello-world/</a>","license":"自由转载-非商用-禁止演绎-保持署名 (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}